    <item>
      <title>1.0.9</title>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <ul>
            <li><strong>New Features:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Queue Auto-Split:</strong> Copied multi-line text can now be automatically split into separate queue items, including single newline-separated lines.</li>
                <li><strong>Queue Controls:</strong> Added a dedicated Auto-Split toggle button in Queue Clipboard controls and shortcut options for Auto-Split and LIFO/FIFO order toggling.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Improvements:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Audio Feedback:</strong> Queue toggles and clear action now play consistent Morse sound feedback.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Bug Fixes:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Paste Without Formatting:</strong> Queue paste now correctly respects the plain-text paste preference.</li>
                <li><strong>General Settings Layout:</strong> Fixed clipping/overflow issues in behavior and custom separator controls in localized UI.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        ]]>
      </description>
