      <title>1.0.7</title>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <ul>
            <li><strong>New Features:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Queue Clipboard Redesign:</strong> A cleaner, modern look with a floating bottom bar for controls and a separate floating clear button.</li>
                <li><strong>LIFO/FIFO Toggle:</strong> You can now switch between Last-In-First-Out (LIFO) and First-In-First-Out (FIFO) paste order in the Queue Clipboard.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Improvements:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Focus Handling:</strong> When using Cmd+C or Cmd+V within the Queue Clipboard, FlashClip now temporarily yields focus to the background app to ensure the action is performed on the correct target.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        ]]>
      </description>
